name: Crush's Coaster
theme: Spin through the East Australian Current with Crush the sea turtle in a thrilling spinning coaster.
short_description: A spinning dark ride roller coaster themed to Finding Nemo.

name: Ratatouille: The Adventure
theme: Shrink to rat size and scurry through Gusteau's kitchen in this trackless 3D adventure with Remy.
short_description: A cutting-edge trackless dark ride through the world of Ratatouille.

name: Toy Soldiers Parachute Drop
theme: Join the Green Army Men on a parachute training mission with gentle drops from above.
short_description: A family-friendly drop tower themed to Toy Story's army men.

name: Slinky Dog Zigzag Spin
theme: Spin around in Slinky Dog's coils as he chases his tail in Andy's backyard.
short_description: A spinning flat ride featuring Toy Story's Slinky Dog.

name: RC Racer
theme: Race back and forth on a giant U-shaped track aboard RC from Toy Story.
short_description: A high-speed shuttle coaster swinging guests on a half-pipe track.

name: Cars Road Trip
theme: Join Lightning McQueen and Mater on a road trip across America in this family dark ride.
short_description: A gentle dark ride through scenes from the Cars films.

name: Cars Quatre Roues Rallye
theme: Spin and whip around in a Cars-themed teacup-style ride.
short_description: A spinning flat ride featuring Cars characters.

name: The Twilight Zone Tower of Terror
theme: Enter the haunted Hollywood Tower Hotel and experience terrifying drops in a service elevator.
short_description: A thrilling free-fall drop tower with randomized drop sequences.

name: Rock 'n' Roller Coaster starring Aerosmith
theme: Launch from 0 to 60 mph through a darkened soundstage with inversions and Aerosmith's music.
short_description: A high-speed launched indoor coaster with loops set to rock music.

name: Animagique
theme: A theatrical celebration of Disney animation featuring Mickey, Donald, and classic films.
short_description: A live stage show celebrating Disney's animated classics.

name: Studio Tram Tour: Behind the Magic
theme: A backlot tour featuring movie sets, props, and special effects including Catastrophe Canyon.
short_description: A guided tram tour through working film sets and special effects.

name: Art of Disney Animation
theme: Explore the animation process through interactive exhibits and drawing classes.
short_description: An educational walk-through showcasing Disney animation techniques.

name: Flying Carpets Over Agrabah
theme: Soar on magic carpets above the rooftops of Agrabah with altitude control.

theme: A live musical celebration of Frozen featuring Anna, Elsa, and the songs of Arendelle.
short_description: A theatrical stage show bringing Frozen to life with music and performances.

theme: Sail through the kingdom of Arendelle experiencing iconic moments from Frozen.

name: Wandering Oaken's Sliding Sleighs

name: The Lion King: Rhythms of the Pride Lands
theme: A theatrical celebration of The Lion King with African rhythms, puppetry, and acrobatics.
short_description: A high-energy live show celebrating The Lion King with music and dance.

name: Disney Junior Dream Factory
theme: An interactive show where young guests dance and play with Disney Junior characters.
short_description: A high-energy dance party for preschoolers with Disney Junior stars.

name: Moteurs... Action! Stunt Show Spectacular
theme: A live-action stunt show featuring high-speed car chases, motorcycles, and pyrotechnics.
short_description: An action-packed live stunt show demonstrating movie car stunts.

theme: Experience a simulated space station destruction with special effects from the film Armageddon.

name: Disney Dreams! of Christmas
theme: A seasonal nighttime spectacular featuring projections, lasers, and Disney holiday magic.
short_description: A Christmas nighttime show celebrating Disney stories with special effects.
